properties.areaDesc: Northern Sangre de Cristo Mountains; Southern Sangre de Cristo Mountains; East Slopes Sangre de Cristo Mountains
properties.headline: High Wind Warning issued January 17 at 3:50AM MST until January 17 at 8:00PM MST by NWS Albuquerque NM
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 35 to 45 mph with gusts up to 65 mph
expected.

* WHERE...Sangre de Cristo Mountains.

* WHEN...From 10 AM this morning to 8 PM MST this evening.

* IMPACTS...High winds may move loose debris, damage property
and cause power outages. Travel will be difficult especially
for high profile vehicles.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Light snow will also be possible through
the afternoon resulting in reduced visibility in blowing snow.
Those travelling around the Enchanted Circle will be impacted.
properties.instruction:
People are urged to secure loose objects that could be blown
around or damaged by the wind.

NWSheadline: HIGH WIND WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM THIS MORNING TO 8 PM MST THIS EVENING
